vc2-reference
------------------------------------------
Reference encoder and decoder for SMPTE ST 2042-1 VC-2 Video Compression

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.9.0-3
  libgcc1-6.4.0-4
  libstdc++6-6.4.0-4

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-10-1
  binutils-2.29-1
  cygport-0.25.0-1
  gcc-core-6.4.0-4
  gcc-g++-6.4.0-4
  libtool-2.4.6-5
  make-4.2.1-2
  python-2.7.14-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/bbc/vc2-reference

Canonical download:
  git://github.com/bbc/vc2-reference.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack vc2-reference-0.1.0.2+git20170629-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./vc2-reference-0.1.0.2+git20170629-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/vc2-reference-0.1.0.2+git20170629-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/vc2-reference-0.1.0.2+git20170629-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(vc2-reference)
  /usr/bin/DecodeStream.exe
  /usr/bin/EncodeHQ-CBR.exe
  /usr/bin/EncodeHQ-ConstQ.exe
  /usr/bin/EncodeLD.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/vc2-reference.README
  /usr/share/doc/vc2-reference/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/vc2-reference/README

------------------

